snippet:
Hoy ha fallecido Mercedes, mi suegra en este centro.
Al respecto,  trato HUMANO, profesional, resilente , empatico y determinacion. Por parte de dos equipos médicos.Estos equipos conformados por doctores, enfermeras, enfermeros, auxiliares, servicios logisticos, etc, a todos ellos GRACIAS.
Capítulo aparte,  es la masificacion en urgencias, competencia del sistema político, que no dota de más personal sanitario, cuando por circunstancias diversas se colapsa URGENCIAS.
Será que no pagamos suficientes impuestos...

extracted_snippet.translated:
Today Mercedes, my mother-in-law in this center, passed away.
In this regard, HUMAN, professional, resilient, empathetic and determination treatment. On behalf of two medical teams. These teams made up of doctors, nurses, assistants, logistical services, etc., THANK YOU to all of them.
A separate chapter is the overcrowding in emergencies, the responsibility of the political system, which does not provide more health personnel, when due to various circumstances, EMERGENCIES collapse.
Maybe we don't pay enough taxes...
